Who made your character’s weapon? The Arc Pistol is a basic model he purchased once he started his current job as a courier for use when the Shirren-Eye is impractical. The Shirren-Eye was also a basic model, but the engraving he commissioned before he left Lajok. It was done by a craftsman by the name of Yorin
